Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.58,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we're different
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.46,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}You think we never feel the way you do
